quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,46,Kandi rwose twahaye Musa ibitangaza byacu tumwohereza kwa Farawo n’ibyegera bye (kugira ngo abahamagarire kuyoboka inzira igororotse). Nuko (Musa) aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri njye ndi intumwa ya Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose.”
  43,47,"Ariko ubwo yabageragaho azanye ibitangaza byacu, barabisetse barabinnyega"
  43,48,"Kandi buri gitangaza twaberekaga (Farawo n’abantu be) cyabaga kiruta kigenzi cyacyo cyakibanjirije (mu kugaragaza ukuri kwa Musa, ariko byose barabihakanye), maze tubahanisha ibihano bihambaye kugira ngo bagarukire Allah"
  43,49,Nuko babwira (Musa) bati “Yewe wa murozi we! Dusabire Nyagasani wawe ku bw’isezerano yaguhaye. Mu by’ukuri (naramuka adukijije ibihano) rwose turayoboka.”
  43,50,"Maze tubakijije ibihano, bica isezerano"
  43,51,Nuko Farawo atangariza abantu be aranguruye ijwi agira ati “Yemwe bantu banjye! Ese si njye ufite ubwami bwa Misiri n’iyi migezi itemba munsi (y’ingoro) yanjye? Ese ntimubona?”
  43,52,"“Ahubwo se si njye muntu mwiza kuruta uyu (Musa) usuzuguritse, ugorwa no kwisobanura?”"
  43,53,"Kuki atamanuriwe ibikomo bya zahabu, cyangwa ngo aze aherekejwe n’abamalayika (bo kumushyigikira)"
  43,54,Nuko (Farawo) agira abantu be ibicucu (arabazindaza) maze baramwumvira. Mu by’ukuri bari abantu b’inkozi z’ibibi
  43,55,"Nuko bamaze kuturakaza twarihoreye, maze tubaroha (mu mazi) bose"
  43,56,Nuko tubagira icyitegererezo n’iciro ry’umugani (ngo babe isomo) ku bazaza nyuma